Subject: Re: [PATCH 8/8] i386: bitops: smp_mb__{before, after}_clear_bit() definitions
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
